you check yourself into

36:36.530 --> 36:38.365
an inpatient program
before you do something

36:38.532 --> 36:40.951
that you cannot take back.

36:42.286 --> 36:44.204
You don't believe me.

36:44.413 --> 36:46.206
(SOFTLY) Please, Ally.

36:46.373 --> 36:48.792
This will give you time
to clear your head.

36:49.751 --> 36:53.797
And it'll look a lot better
if you take this step voluntarily.

37:06.935 --> 37:09.605
(WHISPERS) Fuck you.

37:10.981 --> 37:12.816
(DOOR SLAMS)

37:12.983 --> 37:14.568
(WHISPERS) Damn it.

37:14.735 --> 37:18.488
-(CROWD CHEERING, CLAPPING)
-KAI: What an amazing turnout!

37:18.655 --> 37:20.199
Thank you for taking the time

37:20.365 --> 37:22.993
to be here with your fellow patriots.

37:23.160 --> 37:25.370
-Give yourselves a hand!
-(CHEERING)

37:25.537 --> 37:27.080
Yeah.

37:28.415 --> 37:30.375
<i>Yeah. Thank you.</i>

37:30.542 --> 37:34.505
For those of you who don't know,
my opponent, Sally Keffler,

37:34.671 --> 37:38.634
<i>tragically and unexpectedly</i>
<i>committed suicide last night.</i>

37:38.800 --> 37:42.304
And while no one can truly
understand the despair she felt,

37:42.471 --> 37:45.516
and with my deepest sympathies
for her family,

37:45.682 --> 37:49.728
<i>I pledge to you that I will</i>
<i>never desert you like she did.</i>

37:49.895 --> 37:51.021
(CHEERING)

37:52.856 --> 37:55.442
Give me a close-up.

37:55.609 --> 37:57.694
<i>It takes courage</i>
<i>to stand up for the truth.</i>

37:57.861 --> 37:59.196
-CROWD: <i>Yeah!</i>
-(CHEERING)

37:59.446 --> 38:01.031
This world is a scary place,

38:01.198 --> 38:04.284
and there may be more dangers
out there than I can foresee,

38:04.493 --> 38:08.288
but that's why we need
the strength of our convictions.

38:08.455 --> 38:10.499
-(CHEERING)
-Fundamental truths

38:10.666 --> 38:13.293
we all know in our hearts.

38:13.460 --> 38:16.213
That we were better off
before political correctness...

38:16.380 --> 38:19.508
-Meadow!
-...took over our public discourse.

38:19.716 --> 38:21.718
How about we stand up
for the right of the majority?

38:21.885 --> 38:24.179
America for Americans!

38:24.346 --> 38:26.431
-Excuse me.
-We are the wall!

38:26.598 --> 38:29.685
-Meadow? Meadow, stop.
-(CHEERING)

38:29.852 --> 38:31.520
CROWD: (CHANTING) We are the wall!

38:31.687 --> 38:34.106
-We are the wall!
-KAI: This election isn't the end.

38:34.273 --> 38:36.316
-We are the wall...
-KAI: It's just the beginning.

38:36.483 --> 38:38.652
But it's gonna take
more than just talk.

38:38.819 --> 38:41.613
It's gonna take passion and sacrifice!

38:41.780 --> 38:43.532
I pledge to you...

38:43.699 --> 38:45.784
-I am the promise!
-Stop!

38:45.951 --> 38:47.578
(CHEERING)

38:49.580 --> 38:50.581
(GUNSHOT)

38:53.500 --> 38:56.253
(PANICKED SHOUTS MUTED)

38:56.420 --> 38:57.754
(GUNSHOT)

38:57.921 --> 38:58.922
(DISTORTED, ECHOING)
Down!

38:59.047 --> 39:00.174
(WOMAN'S DISTORTED CRY)

39:00.340 --> 39:02.467
(OVERLAPPING SHOUTING)

39:07.139 --> 39:09.808
(WOMAN'S DISTORTED SCREAM)

39:12.352 --> 39:13.478
Meadow!

39:14.730 --> 39:17.441
Meadow, stop! Stop!

39:18.942 --> 39:19.943
(IVY SHRIEKS)

39:23.238 --> 39:24.865
Meadow, stop!

39:25.073 --> 39:26.450
(WOMAN SCREAMS)

39:26.658 --> 39:27.910
Meadow!

39:28.076 --> 39:30.495
(SIREN WAILING IN DISTANCE)

39:30.662 --> 39:32.289
Meadow, please.

39:32.456 --> 39:34.666
Please, enough. Stop!

39:34.833 --> 39:36.001
Stop.

39:36.168 --> 39:38.170
This is the face of true love.

39:39.630 --> 39:40.756
(GRUNTS)

39:40.923 --> 39:42.424
(SIREN APPROACHING)

39:42.591 --> 39:44.593
MAN 1: Go. Move, move,
move, move, move.

39:44.760 --> 39:46.470
-Drop the gun!
-MAN 2: Drop it! Drop the gun!

39:52.351 --> 39:53.852
(PANTING)

39:55.187 --> 39:57.022
KAI: <i>You don't exist.</i>

39:57.189 --> 39:59.608
You are nothing.

40:04.154 --> 40:07.866
In the eyes
of the unenlightened world.

40:08.033 --> 40:09.785
(SOBS QUIETLY)

40:15.874 --> 40:17.793
(BOX-CUTTER CLATTERS TO FLOOR)

40:23.882 --> 40:26.176
But to me...

40:27.177 --> 40:28.303
you're everything.

40:38.146 --> 40:40.065
You're the only one who sees me,

40:41.441 --> 40:43.902
who's not afraid to see the truth.

40:45.320 --> 40:47.155
You were right...

40:47.322 --> 40:49.157
about all of it.

40:49.992 --> 40:53.954
We have to accelerate our thinking,
get the entire country to pay attention,

40:54.121 --> 40:57.374
elevate me to the <i>national </i>stage.

40:57.541 --> 40:59.334
And only you...

41:00.752 --> 41:03.255
(EXHALES) You can do that.

41:04.548 --> 41:06.008
(PANTS)

41:06.175 --> 41:07.759
-Me?
-KAI: You.

41:07.926 --> 41:10.220
-But how?
-(KISSING)

41:16.602 --> 41:19.521
I need to be... assassinated.

41:21.899 --> 41:24.026
I can't kill you.

41:24.193 --> 41:26.111
(KISSING)

41:26.320 --> 41:28.947
You'll try... and fail.

41:29.531 --> 41:33.368
I'll be shot,
hospitalized, and then recover...

41:33.535 --> 41:35.621
stronger than ever.

41:40.542 --> 41:42.753
We're a Christian country.

41:44.046 --> 41:46.965
Everybody loves a resurrection.

41:47.883 --> 41:50.761
(BOTH GRUNTING)

41:51.887 --> 41:54.932
(MOANING)

41:55.098 --> 41:57.309
But before you do that,

41:57.476 --> 42:00.062
I need you to bear witness.

42:00.229 --> 42:02.439
Which is why
I'm sending you to Ally.

42:02.606 --> 42:04.525
-(MEADOW MOANS)
-(KISSING)

42:04.691 --> 42:07.069
-You want me to lie to her?
-KAI: No.

42:07.236 --> 42:09.363
I want you to tell the truth...

42:09.530 --> 42:11.448
about all of it.

42:11.615 --> 42:13.909
Because when it comes
out of her mouth,

42:14.076 --> 42:16.954
that's when the truth
can hide in plain sight.

42:17.120 --> 42:18.622
(PANTS)

42:18.789 --> 42:21.542
Nobody will believe
what a crazy woman says.

42:21.708 --> 42:23.961
(BOTH MOAN)

42:24.127 --> 42:27.047
You're the only one
I can trust to do this.

42:27.214 --> 42:29.216
(BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY)

42:30.509 --> 42:33.136
-I'm afraid.
-(KAI KISSES, MOANS)

42:33.303 --> 42:35.389
Tell me, my love.

42:36.640 --> 42:37.891
(WHISPERS) Oh, God.

42:38.058 --> 42:39.643
I'll crack under pressure.

42:39.810 --> 42:42.187
-KAI: No.
-I won't be able to lie to the police.

42:42.354 --> 42:45.065
No. You won't have to.

42:45.232 --> 42:47.901
It'll be our eternal secret.

42:48.068 --> 42:51.029
Our everlasting love.

42:51.196 --> 42:52.656
(MOANS)

42:52.823 --> 42:55.576
(WHISPERS) Do you understand?

43:00.122 --> 43:01.957
Yes.

43:10.966 --> 43:13.177
(INDISTINCT RADIO CHATTER)

43:13.343 --> 43:15.304
-OFFICER 1: All right, let's go.
-OFFICER 2: Come on.

43:24.354 --> 43:26.398
(SIREN WAILING IN DISTANCE)

43:50.005 --> 43:52.007
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)
